<span id="an_12:2">12:2</span> Amarja, Maluhx, HXatusx,

<span id="an_12:3">12:3</span> SXehxanja, Rehxum, Meremot,

<span id="an_12:4">12:4</span> Ido, Ginton, Abija,

<span id="an_12:5">12:5</span> Mijamin, Maadja, Bilga,

<span id="an_12:6">12:6</span> SXemaja, Jojarib, Jedaja,

